snippet.title: The Wonton Don
snippet.description:
Donnie Does AKA The Wonton Don is a cultural cosmonaut who travels the globe investigating anything that might make you say "Whoa, That's Weird". He also happens to be a world class crab rangoon chef. This is your one stop shop for travel, humor, and strange tales from the other side of the world. Not your father's travel show.
